 generalized to counter different types of\ninequality, e.g., race, and proactively promote minorities in the society.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Nov 2020 21:06:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 May 2021 15:55:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 15 Oct 2021 21:08:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-19"}
