ecomposable module in\n${\\rm CM}(B_{k,n})$ corresponding to a real root is a cyclic permutation of a\ncanonical profile.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Nov 2020 11:56:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Nov 2020 21:03:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 16 Apr 2022 16:03:22 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 11 May 2023 17:12:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-12"}
