a field theory approach\nthat also assists in understanding certain aspects of OTOC such as the sound\nspeed. Our findings are a step forward towards a more general understanding of\nthe spatio-temporal spread of perturbations in long-range interacting systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Nov 2020 14:43:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-29"}
